thread.title: Q&A: U.S. Expels Russian Diplomats

author: Chris Gordon
title: Q&A: U.S. Expels Russian Diplomats
text:
The U.S. is expelling 60 Russians and closing a Russian consulate in response to the poisoning of a former Russian spy and his daughter in the U.K. earlier this month, which Western countries say was likely ordered by Moscow.
Russia has denied carrying out the Salisbury, England, attack.
